text: Rosalba crassepunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1948. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Rosalba crassepunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1948
title: Rosalba crassepunctata
